## Lists

### Unordered List
```tsx
<ul className="space-y-3">
  <li className="flex items-start gap-3">
    <span className="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-neutral-400 dark:bg-neutral-600 shrink-0" />
    <span className="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
      List item with comfortable spacing and subtle bullet
    </span>
  </li>
</ul>
```

### Ordered List
```tsx
<ol className="space-y-4">
  <li className="flex items-start gap-4">
    <span className="flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white shrink-0">
      1
    </span>
    <div>
      <p className="font-medium text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Step title</p>
      <p className="text-sm text-neutral-700/80 dark:text-white/70 mt-1">
        Step description with additional context.
      </p>
    </div>
  </li>
</ol>
```

### Check List
```tsx
<ul className="space-y-3">
  <li className="flex items-center gap-3">
    <div className="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-neutral-900 dark:bg-white flex items-center justify-center">
      <svg className="w-3 h-3 text-white dark:text-neutral-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth={3}>
        <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <span className="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">Feature or benefit item</span>
  </li>
</ul>
```

