## Spacing & Layout

### Container
```tsx
<div className="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
  {/* Content */}
</div>
```

### Section Spacing
```tsx
<section className="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
  {/* Section content */}
</section>
```

### Content Width Constraints
```css
/* Hero/Large headlines */
max-w-4xl mx-auto

/* Body content */
max-w-3xl mx-auto

/* Narrow content (forms, etc) */
max-w-xl mx-auto
```

### Grid Layouts
```tsx
/* 2-column features */
<div className="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">

/* 3-column cards */
<div className="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

/* 4-column footer links */
<div className="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
```

---

## Animations & Transitions

### Standard Transitions
```css
/* Default for interactive elements */
transition-all duration-300

/* Quick feedback (hover states) */
transition-colors duration-200

/* Shadow changes */
transition-shadow duration-300
```

### Framer Motion Patterns

**Fade In:**
```tsx
initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
transition={{ duration: 0.6 }}
```

**Slide Up:**
```tsx
initial={{ y: 20, opacity: 0 }}
animate={{ y: 0, opacity: 1 }}
transition={{ duration: 0.5, ease: "easeOut" }}
```

**Staggered Children:**
```tsx
// Parent
variants={{
  visible: { transition: { staggerChildren: 0.1 } }
}}

// Child
variants={{
  hidden: { y: 20, opacity: 0 },
  visible: { y: 0, opacity: 1, transition: { type: "spring", stiffness: 150, damping: 25 } }
}}
```

**Spring for Playful Motion:**
```tsx
transition={{
  type: "spring",
  stiffness: 150,
  damping: 25
}}
```

---

## Borders & Shadows

### Border Radius Scale
```css
rounded-lg     /* 0.5rem - inputs, small elements */
rounded-xl     /* 0.75rem - buttons, small cards */
rounded-2xl    /* 1rem - cards, modals */
rounded-[1.15rem] /* Custom for primary buttons */
```

### Shadows
```css
/* Subtle elevation */
shadow-lg

/* Interactive hover */
hover:shadow-xl

/* Dark mode shadow */
dark:hover:shadow-neutral-800/50
```

### Glassmorphism Recipe
```tsx
className="backdrop-blur-md bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/95 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10"
```

---

## Iconography

- Use line icons (stroke-based), not filled
- Consistent stroke width: 1.5 or 2
- Sizes: 16px (inline), 20px (buttons), 24px (standalone)
- Color: Match text color or use muted variant

```tsx
<IconComponent className="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300" strokeWidth={1.5} />
```

---

## Do's and Don'ts

### Do
- Use generous whitespace
- Maintain high contrast for text readability
- Use subtle opacity variations for hierarchy
- Apply glassmorphism sparingly for key interactive elements
- Use spring animations for a premium feel

### Don't
- Use more than 2 font weights per element
- Apply gradient text to body copy
- Use harsh shadows (prefer subtle, diffused shadows)
- Over-animate (reserve motion for meaningful interactions)
- Use colors outside the neutral palette unless intentional accent

---

## Example Page Structure

```tsx
<main className="min-h-screen bg-white dark:bg-neutral-950">
  {/* Hero */}
  <section className="relative py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div className="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 text-center">
      <h1 className="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-900 to-neutral-700/80 dark:from-white dark:to-white/80 mb-6">
        Page Title
      </h1>
      <p className="text-lg text-neutral-700/80 dark:text-white/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Subtitle or description text
      </p>
      {/* Primary CTA button */}
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Features */}
  <section className="py-16 md:py-24 border-t border-black/5 dark:border-white/5">
    <div className="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <h2 className="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-center mb-12">
        Section Title
      </h2>
      <div className="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {/* Feature cards */}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
```